00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:14,300
 So let's just protect those who really need it,

805
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,220
 but if any of you need to get out

806
00:38:16,220 --> 00:38:17,540
 and you don't know what to do,

807
00:38:17,540 --> 00:38:19,260
 please contact our counseling team.

808
00:38:19,260 --> 00:38:21,340
 They would love to,

809
00:38:21,340 --> 00:38:22,900
 all of our trained professional counselors

