00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:41,960
 The perfect, sinless Son of God came to earth

834
00:39:41,960 --> 00:39:45,100
 to experience life on earth to its fullness.

835
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:49,120
 And near the end of his life,

836
